---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Nous soutenir" description="Soutenez l'Étoile Cycliste Ouvrière de Firminy - Sponsoring, mécénat et partenariats">
  <div class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-yellow-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Nous soutenir
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Découvrez comment soutenir l'ECOF à travers le sponsoring, le mécénat et les partenariats
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Sponsoring vs Mécénat -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Sponsoring ou Mécénat ?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Sponsoring -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-red-500">
            <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sponsoring</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Partenariat commercial avec contrepartie publicitaire. Votre entreprise bénéficie d'une visibilité 
                directe auprès de notre communauté de cyclistes et lors de nos événements.
              </p>
              
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Avantages fiscaux :</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Déduction fiscale à 60% du montant
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Plafond : 0,5% du CA HT ou 20 000€
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Reçu fiscal délivré
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contreparties :</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li>• Logo sur les maillots et équipements</li>
                <li>• Visibilité lors des événements</li>
                <li>• Communication sur nos réseaux sociaux</li>
                <li>• Mention dans nos publications</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Mécénat -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-yellow-500">
            <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Mécénat</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Soutien désintéressé à notre association d'intérêt général. Votre contribution aide directement 
                au développement du cyclisme local et à la formation des jeunes.
              </p>
              
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Avantages fiscaux :</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Réduction d'impôt à 66% du montant
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Plafond : 0,5% du CA HT ou 20 000€
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Reçu fiscal CERFA délivré
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reconnaissance :</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li>• Mention sur notre site internet</li>
                <li>• Remerciements lors des événements</li>
                <li>• Rapport d'activité annuel</li>
                <li>• Invitation aux événements du club</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Nos formules de partenariat -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Nos formules de partenariat</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Partenaire Bronze -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-600 to-gray-700 p-6 text-center text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Partenaire Bronze</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">500€</div>
              <p class="opacity-90">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Logo sur le site internet</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Mention réseaux sociaux</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Remerciements événements</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir Bronze
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Partenaire Argent -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-red-500 relative">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <span class="bg-red-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Populaire</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 p-6 text-center text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Partenaire Argent</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">1 500€</div>
              <p class="opacity-90">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Tout Bronze +</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Logo sur les maillots</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Panneau lors des événements</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Newsletter mensuelle</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir Argent
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Partenaire Or -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 p-6 text-center text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Partenaire Or</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">3 000€</div>
              <p class="opacity-90">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Tout Argent +</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Naming d'un événement</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Logo principal sur véhicule</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Événement dédié</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir Or
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Autres formes de soutien -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Autres formes de soutien</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Bénévolat -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-gray-800 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bénévolat</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Donnez de votre temps pour aider lors des événements, l'encadrement ou la maintenance.
            </p>
            <a href="/nous-rejoindre" class="text-gray-800 hover:text-gray-900 font-semibold">
              Devenir bénévole →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Dons matériels -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-red-600 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Dons matériels</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Vélos, équipements, outils... Vos dons matériels sont les bienvenus et déductibles.
            </p>
            <a href="mailto:contact@ecof-firminy.fr" class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-semibold">
              Nous contacter →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Prestations -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-yellow-600 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Prestations</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Offrez vos services professionnels : communication, comptabilité, transport, etc.
            </p>
            <a href="mailto:partenariats@ecof-firminy.fr" class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 font-semibold">
              Proposer ses services →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact partenariats -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-yellow-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Intéressé par un partenariat ?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Contactez-nous pour discuter ensemble de la meilleure formule adaptée à vos besoins et objectifs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="mailto:partenariats@ecof-firminy.fr" class="bg-white text-red-600 hover:bg-gray-100 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Nous contacter
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+33123456789" class="bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors border border-white/30">
            Appeler le club
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>